		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Your sing a song of battle or let out a war cry that empowers one of your allies to become a juggernaut of destruction.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Ally (60 ft.) - 1 Round - Magical</p><p>You expend a use of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.kg7VBahhFH6gDFIh]{Bardic Inspiration} to use this ability. This ability ends early if you use it again or become incapacitated.</p><ul><li><p>Your chosen ally adds your bardic inspiration die to all weapon attack and damage rolls.*</p></li></ul><p>​</p><p><em>*This feature improves at level 10, at which point it adds double your bardic inspiration die to the target's damage rolls. The bonus to attack rolls remains the same.</em></p>",
